CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 19, 1954, page 8 reads: "Thousands Attend Courier Home, Food Show...1. Mrs. Louise R. Prothro, Pet Milk Company Home Economist and Demonstrator for the Courier Home Service Fair preparing one of her delicious recipes, and assisted by Mrs. Mary Ellen Nelson...Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: PET home economist Louise R. Prothro, performing cooking demonstration with assistant Mary Ellen Nelson on stage in Hunt Armory for the 1954 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
